===Etymology===
* First attested in the 1570's.
* From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|for|accoster}}, from {{etyl|VL.|en}} {{m|la|accosto||to come alongside someone}}, from {{m|la|ad||near}} + {{m|la|costa||rib, side}}

